 align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hate Run</span><hr size=1> The only gate potion I can easily obtain now is the Thurg Gate potion, with a 10 second casting time.  Did you use a spell with a similar casting time, or was it an old Cazic Gate potion?<br><br>If it was a Thurg Gate potion, where were you standing when  you gated out? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unarkstackbabber.showPublicProfile?language=EN>NarkStackbabber</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://afi.cinderblock.com/art/sbatguy.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/20/02 9:39:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4461.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hate Run</span><hr size=1> I did this part solo recently also. No deaths, took about 20 minutes. 10 of those minutes were just me trying to get the balls to move from the port-in though. Once I got book, I stood toward the middle of that upper room, so I didn't agro anything through walls, but far enough away from any spawns that were up...I was just a little way in from the table it spawns on. I then cast my Thurg Potion...10 seconds, no agro. Was fairly easy. Good luck.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Nark<br>51 Halfling Garden Tool<br>&lt;Vallis Scortor&gt;<br>Ayonae Ro</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ualkarin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alkarin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/21/02 1:33:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4461.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hate Run</span><hr size=1> I used the Thurgadin Gate Potion. You know the room that's right before the book? It's huge and wide open with no mobs at all, just stand in the corner and gate.<br><br>There was one mob roaming from the bed to the other side, but it was easily avoidable. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showNextMessage?topicID=4461.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4461.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=4461.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.threadControl?topicID=4461.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4461.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4461.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbount